# Assistant config (.claude/, CLAUDE.md) is SHARED with the team in full —
# agents, settings, and agent-memory — so the swarm and its accumulated
# knowledge are reusable by every contributor.

# Editor / LSP config (.vscode, .helix, .editor) is tracked and shared so every
# contributor gets the same four-LSP wiring. Obsidian vault state and the Serena
# symbol cache stay developer-local.
.obsidian/
.serena/

# Nested independently-versioned repos — each has its own .git and its own
# RST-Holdings remote; the meta-repo must NOT track or stage them.
/common-actions/
/docs/
/infrastructure-live/
/routeplane/
/routeplane-skills/
/terraform-modules/
